message:
For each of the files you've identified, make changes to them to run with Starboard as was done with @components/viz/test/run_all_perftests.cc. You can see the changes made to that file with `git diff components/viz/test/run_all_perftests.cc`. The changes you should make are: (1) including "@starboard/client_porting/wrap_main/wrap_main.h", (2) changing the `main` name to `InitAndRunAllTests` and declaring that function static, and (3) adding SB_EXPORT STARBOARD_WRAP_SIMPLE_MAIN(InitAndRunAllTests)

#if !SB_IS(EVERGREEN)
int main(int argc, char** argv) {
  return SbRunStarboardMain(argc, argv, SbEventHandle);
}
#endif to the bottom of each file. If a file with an entry point already uses the STARBOARD_WRAP_SIMPLE_MAIN macro, you don't need to edit it.
